咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T14:12:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/376586225778832/posts/2884907808279982/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F376586225778832%2Fposts%2F2884907808279982%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=FEUhZFrEoh9TukhHyG%2BZyIL97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=ca46ca92\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/376586225778832/posts/2884907808279982/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n理直氣壯"},{"pid":"efc4e26989c190d8293557fc782207b0efb7638d","tid":2103842,"uid":309148,"like":6,"dislike":15,"score":-9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T14:13:00.000Z","msg":"不如俾中六準大學生去決定？<br />\n<br />\n正評：照搞，相信政府，唔會可以拎走我玩+識人嘅機會<br />\n負評： 唔搞，轉形式或者無限期押後（取消）直到疫情完結"},{"pid":"97e9e77d466adeb586ad4a0aa93fea724c3611c9","tid":2103842,"uid":40867,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"efc4e26989c190d8293557fc782207b0efb7638d","tid":2103842,"uid":309148,"like":6,"dislike":15,"score":-9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T14:13:00.000Z","msg":"不如俾中六準大學生去決定？<br />\n<br />\n正評：照搞，相信政府，唔會可以拎走我玩+識人嘅機會<br />\n負評： 唔搞，轉形式或者無限期押後（取消）直到疫情完結"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T14:16:20.000Z","msg":"我支持醉駕合法化<br />\n<br />\n成年人應該有能力決定自己酒後能否渣車<br />\n照渣 相信自己<br />\n到時候撞死人再算 又唔會拎走人地渣車嘅機會"},{"pid":"f8cf5ee94e8b4b94eac2cd3d2541517dacbba69d","tid":2103842,"uid":41484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T14:19:06.000Z","msg":"我就畢業左幾年，其實上年社會事件，理應都已經好多u返唔到學選唔到莊，今年半年無返過學，成支莊運作唔到咁濟仲搞到ocamp?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我見我以前個莊今年選唔到得臨委會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19f937f53c9b5e9d0c324c8e5040d6e29e43c58b","tid":2103842,"uid":315251,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T14:20:19.000Z","msg":"其他搞手都冇諗過咦一個星期突然爆<br />\n我諗都要被啲時間佢哋公佈<br />\n<br />\n我覺得ocamp搞手冇大家想像中咁衰<br />\n佢哋大部分都以fm健康為先<br />\n我諗最後大部份都會唔搞<br />\n即使已經準備好曬啲物資同節目<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"140b3440d651ad577a82d18778b90c3590d70e9a","tid":2103842,"uid":263944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T14:23:04.000Z","msg":"玩Ocam<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d361747b802e613765483fb6321bed9d8ad4adb9","tid":2103842,"uid":58201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T14:46:31.000Z","msg":"喺屋企開cam 玩咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a15902d68570c29b2b56ccd8f228e2644d73484","tid":2103842,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T14:47:29.000Z","msg":"O你老母仲掛住玩<br />\n見間U搞OCAMP我一定小爆佢"},{"pid":"8d408f230d8fcccb303bd895c2e744f734ce409a","tid":2103842,"uid":79731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T14:50:12.000Z","msg":"成條街都係人<br />\nHuman psycho never changes"},{"pid":"81b09a52c2d26e23c9b3b8a56cf861ef065e8f56","tid":2103842,"uid":29929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a15902d68570c29b2b56ccd8f228e2644d73484","tid":2103842,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T14:47:29.000Z","msg":"O你老母仲掛住玩<br />\n見間U搞OCAMP我一定小爆佢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T14:57:40.000Z","msg":"鍵盤小？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"ebdd053a5384e040f6f8696ef8d35a5bcf7707df","tid":2103842,"uid":216910,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T18:49:48.000Z","msg":"想d freshmen融入到咪照開個細組group <br />\n等d fm有connections <br />\n組爸媽WhatsApp 分享下心得先<br />\n疫情好返少少咪自己約出黎組聚比大家認識下<br />\n從來都覺得ocamp 好on9好無聊 <br />\n但以前唔識人又局住要玩<br />\n嗰幾日真係人生最辛苦嘅時候<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都係後續同o mate一齊上堂、食飯先真係firm到"}}